data.description: This immaculate 2023 Highland Home is ready for new owners.  Single-story, 2,377 sq ft home, boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms.  The open living, dining, and kitchen area features a generous island and solid counter tops with gas cooking, high ceilings, and ceramic tiled flooring.  The spacious master bedroom includes a walk-in closet with large bathroom and dual vanity sinks, tiled shower, with separate garden tub. Modern stainless-steel appliances, tankless water heater, and security system make this home ready for new owners.  Seller is offering $5,000 in closing costs.  We look forward to working with you on a smooth transaction.
